{"tid":1923932,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖] 倫敦金仔女又想呃人錢？","createTime":"2020-03-13T11:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T15:50:39.000Z","uid":64854,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5c42669dce4a180a620953966ac83c4d2eb00664","tid":1923932,"uid":64854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:00:33.000Z","msg":"事源係無端端有一男一女打俾我，問我東亞戶口洗唔洗更新番戶口資料，想問我拎個人資料，我緊係無俾到佢。 心諗東亞關我撚事？ 隨後就wts我，又係話自己係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">東亞銀行職員</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (之前自己同東亞無任何關係) 已經覺得鬼鬼地 銀行職員點會無端端用私人號碼wtsapp人 又拎人身份証個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  已報驚  後尾兩條傻閪好緊張咁打電話過嚟屌柒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  用啲爛仔語氣 癲狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  睇得出佢哋好撚心虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家認住呢兩條柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一睇就知又係啲財務中介或者倫敦金啲MK樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XUAco8U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXUAco8U.jpg&h=9f7a2e22&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4TrnMnf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4TrnMnf.jpg&h=0d45ffdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />